content.html: In February 2021 I wrote a piece for Octopus Deploy called "How SpaceX obliterates its competitors and redefines space travel". I was wrong about many things. I've asked the team @OctopusDeploy to take it down. Sometimes the stuff we write just doesn't age well. #Learning
